PREPARE Block 1 > COMMIT Block 1: t2
PRE-PREPARE Block 2 > PREPARE Block 2: t2
PREPARE Block 2 > COMMIT Block 2: t3
PRE-PREPARE Block 3 > PREPARE Block 3: t3
PREPARE Block 3 > COMMIT Block 3: t4

PRE-PREPARE Block 1 --> PRE-PREPARE Block 2: t1
